&lt;p&gt;According to the office of the Registrar of Newspapers for India, the total number of registered newspapers, as on 31 March 2011, was 82,222 (yes, over eighty two thousands). That is newspapers in various vernacular languages and English. Here are just a couple of pictures from the exhibition, for your viewing pleasure.&lt;/p&gt;

