    <id>tag:old.rosettatype.com,2005:NewsPost//2013/12/02/Huronia-posters-published</id>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://old.rosettatype.com/blog#newsDetailSection-2013-12-02-huronia-posters-published"/>
    <title>Huronia posters published</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;With his typeface &lt;a href="http://rosettatype.com/Huronia"&gt;Huronia&lt;/a&gt; Ross Mills takes up the challenge of supporting all native languages of the Americas, with the hope of helping with the preservation of the endangered ones. In order to promote the typeface and its good cause, we decided to design a set of three posters which present native American stories in Cherokee, Nuuchahnulth, and Inuktitut, as well as in English. Anna Giedryś –  the designer of these posters – created beautiful illustrations to accompany each of these stories. Get the posters in &lt;a href="http://rosettatype.com/merchandise"&gt;our merchandise section&lt;/a&gt;. Let us know via email if it is a Christmas gift, we can arrange for express shipping.&lt;/p&gt;
