    <id>tag:old.rosettatype.com,2005:NewsPost//2013/02/02/Eskorte-release</id>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://old.rosettatype.com/blog#newsDetailSection-2013-02-02-eskorte-release"/>
    <title>Eskorte release</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;We have released &lt;a href="http://www.rosettatype.com/Eskorte"&gt;Eskorte&lt;/a&gt;, a new type family by &lt;a href="http://www.rosettatype.com/about&amp;amp;dsg=Schneider"&gt;Elena Scheider&lt;/a&gt;. This ‘fresh and awesome design’, as one of our consultants called it, lends itself equally well to German, Arabic, Czech, Farsi, Urdu, and many other languages. Eskorte is a hardworking type family with an uncomplicated, regular appearance that conveys a crisp, businesslike tone. We have gathered all the information &lt;a href="http://www.rosettatype.com/Eskorte"&gt;on its page&lt;/a&gt; where you can also find the PDF specimen. And finally, we would like to express our thanks to &lt;a href="http://www.rosettatype.com/about&amp;amp;dsg=Nemeth"&gt;Titus Nemeth&lt;/a&gt; for consulting, &lt;a href="http://www.rosettatype.com/about&amp;amp;dsg=Apelian"&gt;Khajag Apelian&lt;/a&gt; for proofreading and testing, and to Georg Seifert and his &lt;a href="http://www.glyphsapp.com"&gt;Glyphs application&lt;/a&gt; for help with production of the fonts.&lt;/p&gt;
