    <id>tag:old.rosettatype.com,2005:NewsPost//2012/05/02/Voice-of-America</id>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://old.rosettatype.com/blog#newsDetailSection-2012-05-02-voice-of-america"/>
    <title>Voice of America</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Nassim is becoming the number one font for Arabic and Persian news around the world. We are proud to announce that the renowned &lt;a href="http://ir.voanews.com"&gt;Persian news-portal Voice of America&lt;/a&gt; has selected Nassim as the main font in their new design. The most important reasons for its adoption are its superior readability in long texts on screen and the genuine Arabic/Persian look. In the words of VOA designers: “you have no idea what you have done for the improvement of the Arabic/Persian web experience”. Well, it is an absolute pleasure to be of help.&lt;/p&gt;
