    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://old.rosettatype.com/blog#newsDetailSection-2011-04-04-new-skolar-web-release"/>
    <title>New Skolar Web release</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;We are happy to present Skolar Web, the successful type family by David Březina manually hinted by Ross Mills. Manual hinting of a font dramatically improves its appearance on computer screens and allows for a superior performance in the web environment. The process fixes alignment problems, improves spacing and generates better consistency between lettershapes. The fonts support extended Latin as well as Cyrillic and are now available from &lt;a href="http://fontdeck.com/typefaces"&gt;Fontdeck&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="http://blog.typekit.com/2011/03/16/skolar-web-hinted-for-better-screen-rendering"&gt;Typekit&lt;/a&gt;, and soon from &lt;a href="http://www.webink.com"&gt;WebInk&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
    <updated>2014-07-24T00:00:00Z</updated>
    <author>
      <name>David Březina</name>
    </author>
