    <id>tag:old.rosettatype.com,2005:NewsPost//2011/04/01/Nassim-sets-news-in-Persian</id>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://old.rosettatype.com/blog#newsDetailSection-2011-04-01-nassim-sets-news-in-persian"/>
    <title>Nassim sets news in Persian</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;The BBC Persian website follows its Arabic sister site in choosing Nassim to deliver its news. Titus Nemeth redraw Nassim to give the website a distinctly Iranian look, whilst maintaining the coherence with the BBC brand visual language. He worked in close collaboration with the Persian language service, and supported his decisions with historical research. See the screenshots in an updated &lt;a href=""&gt;Type in use article&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
