    <title>Two lectures in Cieszyn</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;David gave two lectures in Cieszyn (Poland).The first was called “On Skolar”, and the other talk focused on the process of designing typefaces. The lectures were presented to the students of the Sign and typography studio from the Fine Arts Academy in Poznań.&lt;/p&gt;
