    <title>Two talks for TeX users</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;David gave two lectures; one on issues in multi-script typography and the second one on Skolar and type design for academic publications on the 4th International ConTeXt Meeting and 3rd TeXperience Conference. The events took place in Czech Republic, 13–19 September, one followed by the other.&lt;/p&gt;
